Shell
It is a program that allows interaction between user and operating system.


/home
home directory which is created by the system.
home directory allows to store the personal data in form of files.
Each user in system gets own home directory which is able to store/retrieve the data.

Home directory is represented by tilde(~) symbol.


command and argument
command <options> argument-----> echo -n hello
command = echo
options = -n
argument = hello



Command Types
1. Internal or Built-in commands: echo,cd,pwd,set......etc
2. External Commands: mv,date,cp,uptime.....etc

To Check external or internal command------> type <command>

